description:
F*CK Corona - LOVE nature! 😉
I am still pissed off due to all this corona shit. 🤬 No cultural highlights this summer - a disaster for all the great bands, crews, promoters, athletes and many more! 😔
.
Nevertheless I am happy to have more time for my studies (traditional healer) now. Moreover, I can spend more time outside and enjoy the beautiful nature. 😍 And I have ordered a bunch of CDs (e.g. from Terror, Nasty, Deez Nuts and Lordi 👊). Yeah!!! 🤩
.
Life could be worse! I am healthy, I am still earning money, and I can  listen to my favorite music! 😃🎶
